	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">S.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Scripseram has proxime missurus per quandam mulierem; sed antequam me expedire possem, ipsa discesserat.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Nunc tamen eas, sicut tum occluseram, mitto; nec enim habeo, quod illis addam, nisi quod interea tuas per <persName type="auto_name">Samuelem Hauserum</persName>, agri nostri ministrum, missas accepi una cum aliis ex <placeName ref="l646" cert="high">Clarona</placeName> missis.</s>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Accepit quoque senatus noster per eundem literas <placeName ref="l646" cert="high">Claronensium</placeName> fidelium.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="manual">Illis per hunc cursorem, qui has defert, respondetur; quid respondeatur, plene non scio, hoc tamen scio, <foreign xml:lang="de">das man si manet, das si mitt ir antwort nitt ylind, bis si wüssen mögind, was die Lender<note xml:id="fn1" type="footnote" n="1">Die drei katholischen Landorte Uri, Schwyz und Unterwalden (vgl. <bibl>SI</bibl> III 1298).</note> antwortind, damitt der unwill dest minder uff si falle.</foreign></s>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Imm übrigen sind m[ine] h[erren] der mittlen auch vast übel zfriden, und hörend die botten bi mengklichem übel.</s>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="de" type="auto">J[unker] <persName ref="p7879" cert="high">Niclaus</persName> sorget den krieg, wo si nitt angnommen werdind; wir sorgend aber, förcht ich, vil z'vil, da wir der sorgen nitt halb dörftind, und da wir wol sorgen sottend, da ist nieman daheim.</s>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Oblique audio etiam moneri <placeName type="auto_name">Glaronenses</placeName>, ne recipiant media; puto idem a vestris fieri.</s>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Oremus dominum.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Expecto, ut per hunc de comitiis principum scribas.</s>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Habemus quaedam, quę <persName ref="p8055" cert="high">Blaurerus</persName> scripsit, quę te quoque, quoniam illi longe vicinior es, habere quoque puto; alioqui ea ad te mitterem.</s>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Vale.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName ref="l41" cert="high">Bernę</placeName> 13. martii.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="14" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Salutant te nostri omnes, praesertim <persName type="auto_name">Samuel Zehender</persName>, qui mihi haec scribenti affuit.</s>
					<s n="15" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName ref="p8018" cert="high">I[oannes] Hall[erus]</persName> tuus.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="16" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Clarissimo viro d. Bullingero, domino suo honorando et compatri charissimo.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="17" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName ref="l587" type="auto_name">Tiguri</placeName>.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
		</body>
	</text>
